				<h2 class="post-title">S. Korea’s ruling party thinks Korean journalists must “contribute to peaceful reunification, national reconciliation &#038; the restoration of national homogeneity”</h2>

									<div class="post-excerpt"><p>I often reflect on how life has been kind to me lately. Once, I was poor and cold; now, I live in comfort and warmth. Once, I struggled to eat enough; now, I struggle to eat less. Once, life was enclosed in the ennui of poverty, isolation, and the prospect of a life lived in dullness and pointlessness; now, life is endlessly interesting. Once, I was alienated and alone; now, I come home to my best friends, including the two&#46;&#46;&#46;</p>
